column5: You could try to tell them
How do you think they would react if you explained exactly how you feel and why to them
Do they know how unhappy you are?
Can you be yourself around at least one person in your life?
The best advice i can give you is to keep socializing.
Wanna talk?

Wanna talk? It can be about anything. Let's just have a talk.

Message me if you ever feel like it.

Also, here's my email: [felixlarocque21@gmail.com](mailto:felixlarocque21@gmail.com)

I think you still haven't given up.
Thank you.
Hey, sounds like you really gave up, you remind me of my friend, would you like to talk?  It can be about anything.

You make me wanna cry, honestly. I thought about losing everything but i have nothing, in my head i'm already dead, i sometimes forget that i'm really who i am. I truly have given up and i decided i would just do whatever i wanted as long as i didn't hurt others until i didn't want to go on.
Have you given up?
I don't deserve you, i wish you the best.
Thanks for trying to help... i don't know what to say, i really appreciate it but i don't want to keep going. I think i'm gonna end it next year. I'm so sorry.
Holy fuck thats the funniest shit ive heard
Dont worry im good for now
Ayt thanks
Same reason why i dont say anything to my mom
I can't now but im free tomorrow and th day after.
Yeah lets do it tell me when youre free and ill find a way to talk to you.

Maybe its cause deep down, we're still hoping to find what were searching for, i know thats how it is for me, i cant bring myself to commit suicide because i still hold on to the thought of finding someone who can help me. Even if i havent found that person or thing yet.

I ain't giving up on you, i know how you feel, i was bullied when i was younger because i was akward as fuck. Also, french is my native language so i understand that its not fun to speak english with someone you dont know. Tell me when you're ready to talk.
Yeah i get it
Well i dont eat much.
Gotta go to sleep cause its really late where i live but i would like to talk sometime.
Holy shit i get you, but its only let down after let down, right? Everytime i look forward to something. I guess its our job to find a reason to live.
Whats your native language?
I just hope you get better no matter what happens or what you do, why are we so powerless. Fuck i hate it and i wish i could help
Thats why i hate going to sleep, i know im gonna wake up the next day.
Make this a post for infinite karma
Im just really happy for him homie
